            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>The End of Semester Examination will be held during the end of semester examination period. It will be an in-person exam held on campus.</p>\n<p>The End of Semester Examination will cover the content of the course, as covered in Self-paced Learning,  live lectures and applied classes. You will be provided with a sheet of all the required formulas and a sheet of output from R probability functions.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
